Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:35.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs28\shad0}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N头上的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在高度9500飞行中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,风速0.5至6
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,状态 没有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:39.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,随航机 不要掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:40.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:42.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行程序 CHECK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,接驳主电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,启动回转系统
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:47.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,打开平衡控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:51.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,发电系统转为RG模式 启动各控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,电离子容器压力如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尚未达到3%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只能勉强达到极限压力 我会尽量想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:01:59.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要解开钢索 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:09.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:13.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,5秒前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:14.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,4~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:16.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,3~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,2~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:19.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,1~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,9000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:28.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,8500
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,8000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,7500
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,7000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,6500
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,6000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,米诺夫斯基粒子压缩器正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:58.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,电离子推进力与预测值差别很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:00.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,回转系统也基本没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,震动比想像中的要轻微
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,开始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:24.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是... 哥哥的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看啊 死神还真勤劳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:52.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲还真可怜呢 被这种瘟神缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 让人同情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:01.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要克死多少同伴才肯罢休？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,新手的队长先生就像是来送死的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 军 军曹...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 有这种部下太不幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,军曹...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！死神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长~ 队长~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,头痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 你在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,死神在打架？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是07小队那一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:42.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要买趁早 不快点的话就打完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:43.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里打架？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,10点钟方向 大概380米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 以前军曹所在的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是全军覆没了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁说的这种无聊话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,07小队太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是死神 就要像个死神的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,给我长眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请让开 让开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然3个一起上！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙啊！你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在吵什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是消遣活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,正在加深小队间的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交流？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交流打架经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:36.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,07小队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,先遣的西部地区的后方支援怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 这就出动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 08小队也要准备好能随时出动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:48.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去 你们都回自己的岗位去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 别给死神缠住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,新兵先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊的中伤罢了 别放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:27.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,眼看APSARAS计划的第1阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在诸位的同心协力之下完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS的完成在即
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,完成之后 地球圈的势力图就会被大大地改写
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利一定会在我们吉翁的旗帜下闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了光辉的吉翁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:51.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吉翁万岁~！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:03.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所以德金公王才会将这项计划交由我全权负责
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(是爱娜小姐)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(这可真是...)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(真漂亮 真是漂亮啊~)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就属你最美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的首次试飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,意义重大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,带给了我无比的惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:29.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,空调的状态现在还差了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,出了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能享用美味的饮品 真是令人高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亚斯在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:55.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里·凯拉尼将军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 让开 让出条路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亚斯 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多人面前 不要这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 没关系的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:15.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你造出了不得了的玩具 我特地从欧洲赶了过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,玩具!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个爱娜已经变得这么有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,上次见面时还只是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,女人真是可怕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,凯拉尼大人也变得器宇不凡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 那种恭维说话不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,做我的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:52.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不帮那个执着于萨哈林之名的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你也能一生快快乐乐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的空气好像很差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是傲慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 没趣的兄妹俩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在明明是关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:35.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有那个人在 总是让哥哥无法保持理智
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我若是哥哥的话早就教训他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:40.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐为何会到这里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了哥哥的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那样说很奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:50.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要是哥哥的APSARAS完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战火就会平息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:56.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:10:01.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个无疑是件会夺去很多生命的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了萨哈林家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:07.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后 我也将和萨哈林家共存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 诺里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尊严、名誉、血统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,萨哈林家的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是个人偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不驾驶MS了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能够转职
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚 你来代替我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说 说什么呢... 我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我来驾驶好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,作为机师...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己觉得不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让大家因我而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还在说这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你所在部队全军覆没的确是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可你被07小队的家伙戏弄一下就生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不就等于承认了自己是死神吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所 所以 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不干难道就没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个没有种的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你也有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:41.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种没志气的队员我才不稀罕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止 曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:52.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我所属的部队...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全都在第3次出击时全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不祥的第3次...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:07.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,留我在08小队里的话 大家都会因此而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才不想驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:15.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你把同伴的死当成是自己背负的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说你还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是行动中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你的转职请求是无法接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,回你的岗位去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:35.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会破除掉那种无聊的迷信的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有不妙的预感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明天最好也没有战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想要活着的话 彼此间没有信任怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是信赖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是到达极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,遥测仪也有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,联络各个部队尽可能将防卫线扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,确保APSARAS的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诺里斯 告诉我机体的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 现在还看不出什么特别的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 继续测试负荷率
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:56.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐 请不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:13:59.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙的目的到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:16.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 现在开始向376地区移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:17.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我来带头 你跟着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:21.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讨厌的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,写遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啧 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,机体再次剧烈震动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:43.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 高度4000
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,超负荷严重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,无法控制姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,急速下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,把高度输入操控电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,进入了联邦的势力圈 警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,高度没有上升
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:56.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想办法停止下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,散布米诺夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我到高空去联络基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,东北方的防卫线现在有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 已经开始了骚扰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 基尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该让爱娜撤出了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以放弃APSARAS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜的话应该能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是随航机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时是成功阻止了下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 爱娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,预备部队也一起出动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:44.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,将APSARAS飞行路线上的联邦的耳目引开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:50.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,唉呀呀 天才太过于自信的话 可没有好结果的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:52.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:53.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姿势控制器大致回复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,发信系统恢复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:02.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我也差不多是时候得回欧洲战线去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙能用时就送去我那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是为了你这种人而造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 天才君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚 能测定敌人的位置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,11点钟方向 约2000
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在卡莲在追击他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:31.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 敌人正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就好比是在引诱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 哪里不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什... 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 怎么办 追上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 请听听这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(东面 25公里 布防完毕)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:00.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(明白)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:04.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(保护好APSARAS...)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(沿着丛林...)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(要尽快扫清APSARAS的航路)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,由于有米诺夫斯基粒子在干扰 我听不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看来敌人有东西正向这边过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 为何不用暗号？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们在这里伏击那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全员降低态势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西 真的会过来这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:41.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,它正在过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 40秒后会经由东上空到达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,让它过去 静观其变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说这就是军曹的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到气压震动 相当庞大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:01.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不是MS的体积
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有复数个战斗机的引擎声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:16.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:19.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:22.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,测定射程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,马上清扫APSARAS的航路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋为什么开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎... 怎么办...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冲过来了 散开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,做了多余的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会死的 好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 军... 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:14.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好... 好大...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么家伙呀!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:51.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诺里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 爱娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还能返航吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:03.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事 爱娜小姐 请您撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我来掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁那时候撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会让任何人死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,多么的卤莽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:11.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 我... 才不是死神！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:27.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,输了？怎么能输 我... 我怎么能输！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,射击 不停地射击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,射击直到枪身过热为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:42.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爱娜小姐 再接近会有危险 请您尽快撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着喔 军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:15.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 还活着...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:19.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,得 得救了...
